# Root build context for hub/Dockerfile (cleanslate0 hub_rebase — context widened
# from hub/ to the repo root so npm workspaces resolve @apnex/* natively).
# Keep the uploaded context small: deps are installed in-container via npm ci
# from the committed root lockfile, and dist is built in-container.
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/*.tgz
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
# scratch / local-only
coverage
.claude
